node.title: My babies. 1 year ago. My Kob-Kob and My Gigi

node.text: I was reluctant to get away but I’m so glad I did it! It was so nice to enjoy life a little bit and not think about everything I have on my plate. This was so good for my soul. Thank you so much for an amazing weekend Domenico & Stefano @dolcegabbana ❤️🇮🇹
